e failure persisted on re-run, ruling out a transient/flaky failure."}, {"quote": "self.assertEqual(tcl.eval(r'set a \"<\\ud83d\\udcbb>\"'), '<\\U0001f4bb>')", "reason": "Shows the test expects surrogate pairs to be recombined into a single code point, but the actual result keeps them as surrogates."}], "suggested_fix": "Investigate how CPython's _tkinter decodes Tcl string results containing surrogate pairs under Tcl 9.0.3 on Windows, and update either the decoding logic or the test expectations to match the actual behavior of Tcl 9.0.3's Unicode handling.", "input": {"context_path": "results/v2/stress/hybrid-grep-4k-rtk-err-cat-v1/cpython-tcl-windows-matrix-v2-001.txt", "context_tokens_estimate": 7516}, "usage": {"processing_tokens_estimate": 0, "output_tokens_estimate": 892}, "metadata": {"provider": "command", "prompt_sha256": "ecffdf03c99a91b0f8f75e086720d9fb8db96af0d9dae5285baf679c9c9d28de", "runtime_ms": 27864.904, "cache_key": "8f1abb142488d66132f8df5f1d3b76dc0bef08c3774ed33a1856ec681df09642", "provider_error": null, "provider_error_detail": null, "command": "python3 /Users/eyuansu62/llm_judge/cli-token-killer/cilog-bench/examples/diagnosis_shim_claude_agent.py", "model_info": {"provider_name": "anthropic", "requested_model": "claude-sonnet-4-6", "resolved_model": "claude-sonnet-4-6", "base_url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1", "usage": {"input_tokens": 38412, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 865, "service_tier": "standard", "inference_geo": "global"}}, "diagnoser_config_name": null, "diagnoser_config_sha256": "a87dd5e5ce51e6205be617b7a3c45c1647376786e44852f4b639352884f6c1ea", "shim_sha256": "9d926e0343b984d1ae4eacaf2f824d2bb26a2187b40521325c01423354e61901"}, "agent_metadata": {"iterations": 3, "tool_call_count": 3, "tool_calls": [{"tool": "grep", "args": {"pattern": "error|failed|failure|FAILED|Error", "max_matches": 30}, "obse